title: Stand Together
text:
Influence.
While you control 2 or more Specter units, this objective contributes 2 Force icons to your side during the Force struggle.

title: Ezra Bridger
text: Reaction: After this unit is focused to strike, your opponent must choose to either place 1 focus token on one of his participating units or discard 2 cards at random from his hand.

title: Loth-cat
text:
No enhancements.
Interrupt: When a Specter or neutral unit you control is targeted by an enemy card effect, shuffle this unit into your deck to cancel that effect.

title: Stolen Helmet
text:
Enhance a Specter or Character unit.
Reaction: After a card is discarded from an opponent's hand, draw 1 card. (Limit once per phase.)

title: Improvised Demolition
text: Action: Each Specter and neutral unit you control gains [Blast Damage] until the end of the phase. An opponent may discard 2 cards from his hand at random to cancel this effect. (Limit 1 per turn.)

title: Specter's Concentration
text: If you control a participating Specter unit and your opponent has 3 or fewer cards in hand, this card gains +3 Force icons for this edge battle.

title: Hera Syndulla
text:
Each other friendly Specter and neutral unit gains [Unit Damage].
Reaction: After you refresh, remove 1 focus token from a friendly Specter unit.

title: Ghost
text:
Elite.
Protect Specter.
Interrupt: When a Specter or [Rebel Alliance] unit is targeted by an enemy card effect, focus this unit to cancel that effect. Then, draw 1 card.

title: Phantom
text: Interrupt: When a friendly Specter or Character unit would be destroyed or captured, instead sacrifice this unit and remove all damage from that unit.

title: Hidden Outpost
text:
Enhance your play area.
Limited. (You cannot play more than one limited card per turn.)

keywords.text: You cannot play more than one limited card per turn.

title: Call to Action
text:
Each Specter unit gains [Blast Damage] while this mission is in your victory pile.
Reaction: After this mission is completed, return a target enemy unit to its owner's hand.

title: On the Run
text:
Smugglers and Spies affiliation only.
Reaction: After you reveal 1 or more [Smugglers and Spies] fate cards in your edge stack, look at the top card of your deck. Then, you may place that card into your edge stack.

title: BoShek
text:
Elite.
Edge (X).
X is the number of fate cards in your discard pile (to a maximum of 3).

title: R4-E1
text:
Limited.
Interrupt: When you discard your edge stack, spend 1 resource to return 1 [Smugglers and Spies] card from that edge stack to its owner's hand.

title: Make Your Own Resources
text: Reaction: After you win an edge battle by 2 or more Force icons, put a resource generating card into play from your hand or discard pile.

title: Tricks and Nonsense
text: If your opponent's edge stack contains 1 or more [Scum and Villainy] or neutral cards, your opponent cannot trigger abilities during this engagement.

title: Tricks and Nonsense
text: If your opponent's edge stack contains 1 or more [Scum and Villainy] or neutral cards, your opponent cannot trigger abilities during this engagement.

title: Lure of the Lost
text: Reaction: After you refresh, focus this objective to shuffle 1 card from your discard pile back into your deck.

title: Rav Naaran
text: Reaction: After a unit leaves play during the conflict phase, deal 1 damage to a target enemy objective. (Limit once per turn.)

title: Berserk Hunter
text: Forced Reaction: After this unit resolves a strike, sacrifice it.

title: Berserk Hunter
text: Forced Reaction: After this unit resolves a strike, sacrifice it.

title: Naaran's Lightsaber
text:
Enhance a Force User or Force Sensitive unit.
Enhanced unit gains edge (1).
If enhanced unit is Rav Naaran, he also gains: "Reaction: After a unit leaves play during the conflict phase, deal 1 damage to a target enemy unit. (Limit once per turn.)"

title: Twist of Fate
text: Cancel this edge battle and the card effects of all other fate cards just revealed. Discard both edge stacks and start a new edge battle.

title: Cloud Cover
text: Each piloted Fighter unit you control gains +1 damage capacity.

title: "Howlrunner"
text: Pilot (2). (Each Fighter unit you control gains [Unit Damage].)

keywords.text: Each Fighter unit you control gains [Unit Damage].

title: "Night Beast"
text: Pilot (1). (Reaction: After enhanced Fighter unit survives an engagement as a defender, remove 1 focus token from it.)

keywords.text: Reaction: After enhanced Fighter unit survives an engagement as a defender, remove 1 focus token from it.

title: Obsidian Leader
text:
Targeted strike.
Each Fighter unit you control gains "protect Obsidian Leader" while this unit is piloted.

title: Obsidian 2
text: While this unit is piloted, double its unit damage icons.

title: Stay on Target
text: You may put a Pilot card into play from your hand or discard pile as an enhancement on a target friendly Vehicle unit.
